{"content": "I need to multiply 678 \u00d7 286 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 678\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 486 + 63 + 8 = 557\u2081\u2080\n- 286\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 162 + 72 + 6 = 240\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 557 \u00d7 240 = 133,680\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 133680 \u00f7 9 = 14853 r 3\n- 14853 \u00f7 9 = 1650 r 3\n- 1650 \u00f7 9 = 183 r 3\n- 183 \u00f7 9 = 20 r 3\n- 20 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 2\n- 2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: **223333\u2089**\n\n223333", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}